               <head>Two works</head>
               <msContents class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2009123573 ">
                  <summary>Two works on astrology and geomancy. Other contents: 173v-175v, an excerpt from Asmār al-ashjār; 175v-176v, Dar bayān-i sahm al-sa‘āda; 177r, text on geomancy crossed out; 195v-196v, various short extracts. Undated: late 13th/19th or early 14th/20th century. Light blue paper watermarked ‘C. Millington London’. Purchased from Christie's (8 October 2010, part of Lot 22). </summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2007101548 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2001000141" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Or_16813-item1">
                     <locus from="2v" to="173r">ff. 2v-48r, 50r-173r</locus>
                     <note>
                        <p>A treatise on astrology, without chapter divisions. By Muḥammad Ḥusaynī, called Sayyid Munajjim (alive in 803/1400-1). See Storey PL II/1, C, pp. 65-66. BL copy: Or. 5587, text 1. This copy includes special charts (f. 152, 168) and diagrams. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_7849">Laṭāʾif al-kalām fī aḥkām al-aʿvām</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_7849">لطائف الکلام فی احکام الاعوام</title>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656485.0x000001 viaf_223802442">Sayyid al-Munajjim</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="supplied" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656485.0x000001 viaf_223802442">محمد حسینی سید المنجم</persName>
                     </author>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85054121 " n="2" xml:id="Uk_Or_16813-item2">
                     <locus from="177v" to="195v">ff. 177v-195v</locus>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" type="supplied" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656316.0x000001 viaf_114145003295161300338">Shīrvānī, ʿAbd al-Ghanī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="per" type="supplied" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164656316.0x000001 viaf_114145003295161300338">‏شيروانى، عبد الغنى</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22155">Anvār-i raml</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Treatise on geomancy, comprising a muqaddima, two maqāla, and a khātima. By ‘Abd al-Ghanī Ḥāfiẓ Shīrvānī. See Storey, PL II/3, J, p. 483. Published Lucknow, 1294/1877. Very incomplete copy: beginning only. </p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="per">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
